```

**Key Drag and Drop Events:**

| Event | Trigger | Purpose |
|-------|---------|----------|
| `dragstart` | Drag begins | Set drag data and visual feedback |
| `drag` | During drag | Continuous feedback |
| `dragenter` | Enter drop zone | Visual feedback for valid drop |
| `dragover` | Over drop zone | Must prevent default to allow drop |
| `dragleave` | Leave drop zone | Remove visual feedback |
| `drop` | Item dropped | Handle the drop operation |
| `dragend` | Drag ends | Clean up |

**DataTransfer Methods:**
- `setData(format, data)`: Store data for the drag operation
- `getData(format)`: Retrieve data during drop
- `setDragImage(element, x, y)`: Set custom drag image
- `effectAllowed`: Set allowed drag effects
- `dropEffect`: Set current drop effect

**Use Cases:**
- File uploads with drag and drop
- Sortable lists and tables
- Kanban boards
- Image galleries
- Form builders
- Dashboard widgets

