.justify-end { justify-content: flex-end; }        /* Items at end */
.justify-center { justify-content: center; }       /* Items in center */
.justify-between { justify-content: space-between; } /* Equal space between */
.justify-around { justify-content: space-around; }  /* Equal space around */
.justify-evenly { justify-content: space-evenly; }  /* Equal space everywhere */
```

**4. Align-Items Examples (Cross Axis):**

```css
/* Vertical alignment when flex-direction: row */
.align-start { align-items: flex-start; }   /* Items at top */
.align-end { align-items: flex-end; }       /* Items at bottom */
.align-center { align-items: center; }      /* Items in middle */
.align-stretch { align-items: stretch; }    /* Items fill height */
.align-baseline { align-items: baseline; }  /* Items align to text baseline */
```

