**CSS-in-JS** is a pattern where CSS is composed using JavaScript instead of defined in external files. It enables dynamic styling and component-scoped styles.

**Popular CSS-in-JS Libraries:**
- **styled-components** - Template literals
- **Emotion** - Similar to styled-components
- **JSS** - JavaScript object syntax
- **Aphrodite** - Inline styles with CSS features

**Styled-components Examples:**
```javascript
import styled, { css } from 'styled-components';

// Basic styled component
const Button = styled.button`
  background: #007bff;
  color: white;
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;

  &:hover {
    background: #0056b3;
  }
`;

// Props-based styling
const StyledButton = styled.button`
  background: ${props => props.primary ? '#007bff' : '#6c757d'};
  color: white;
  padding: ${props => props.large ? '1rem 2rem' : '0.5rem 1rem'};
  border: none;
  border-radius: 4px;

  ${props => props.outlined && css`
    background: transparent;
    color: ${props.primary ? '#007bff' : '#6c757d'};
    border: 2px solid ${props.primary ? '#007bff' : '#6c757d'};
  `}

  &:disabled {
    opacity: 0.6;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }
`;

// Usage
function App() {
  return (
    <div>
      <Button>Basic Button</Button>
      <StyledButton primary>Primary</StyledButton>
      <StyledButton primary outlined>Outlined</StyledButton>
      <StyledButton large>Large Button</StyledButton>
    </div>
  );
}
```

**Advanced styled-components Features:**
```javascript
// Extending styles
const BaseButton = styled.button`
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;
`;

const PrimaryButton = styled(BaseButton)`
  background: #007bff;
  color: white;
`;

// Theming
import { ThemeProvider } from 'styled-components';

const theme = {
  colors: {
    primary: '#007bff',
    secondary: '#6c757d',
    success: '#28a745'
  },
  breakpoints: {
    mobile: '576px',
    tablet: '768px',
    desktop: '992px'
  }
};

const ThemedButton = styled.button`
  background: ${props => props.theme.colors.primary};
  color: white;

  @media (min-width: ${props => props.theme.breakpoints.tablet}) {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
  }
`;

// App with theme
function App() {
  return (
    <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
      <ThemedButton>Themed Button</ThemedButton>
    </ThemeProvider>
  );
}
```

